name: Pongs Squad - Bubbly
description:
Pongs Squad is a group of criminals from an unknown country. They are scattered in various parts of the world due to a dispute between their captain and vice-captain.

Karl Keith is the healer of this group. He was nicknamed Bubbly. He is one of the distant relatives of the captain. The eyes on his face can heal all kinds of wounds. Even at one time, he had saved Frutty Frut when his body was split open by a samurai attack in Japan. His body could exchange someone's life on the condition that he had to do it in a toilet. Currently, he is hiding somewhere in Malta.
